Sundanese numerals (Sundanese language: Wilangan) is a number system used by Sundanese people and contains a sequence of 10 digits (᮰ ᮱ ᮲ ᮳ ᮴ ᮵ ᮶ ᮷ ᮸ ᮹) in Sundanese script. The Wilangan writing system is the same as in Arabic numerals, i.e. the writing is directed to the right, only there is a difference in terms of marking, namely that the writing of numbers in Sundanese script must use a pipe sign ( | ), because some forms of Sundanese numerals are similar to consonant letters (ᮍᮜᮌᮦᮔ ngalagéna), it is feared that ambiguity will occur.Example: || = 2020
However, because the writing system that is more often used in Sundanese is the Latin alphabet, it is more common to write numbers in Sundanese using Arabic numerals and the use of numbers in Sundanese script is optional.

Basic numbering in Sundanese
Some numbers in Sundanese have more than one different way of pronouncing the number, for example in the tweens, the way of pronouncing the numbers 21–29 can also use lilikuran.
Examples of Writing and Mentioning:

Hundreds
100 – |᮱᮰᮰| – saratus
175 – |᮸᮲᮰| – saratus tujuh puluh lima/lebak satak
200 – |᮲᮰᮰| – dua ratus
300 – |᮳᮰᮰| – tilu ratus
375 – |᮳᮷᮵| – tilu ratus tujuh puluh lima/lebak samas
400 – |᮴᮰᮰| – opat ratus, samas
500 – |᮵᮰᮰| – lima ratus
600 – |᮶᮰᮰| – genep ratus
705 – |᮷᮰᮵| – tujuh ratus lima
800 – |᮸᮰᮰| – dalapan ratus/domas
820 – |᮸᮲᮰| – dalapan ratus dua puluh
999 – |᮹᮹᮹| – salapan ratus salapan puluh salapan

Thousands
1.000 – |᮳᮰᮰᮰| – sarébu
2.000 – |᮲᮰᮰᮰| – dua rébu
3.007 – |᮳᮰᮰᮷| – tilu rébu tujuh
4.010 – |᮴᮰᮱᮰| – opat rébu sapuluh
5.500 – |᮵᮵᮰᮰| – lima rébu lima ratus
6.708 – |᮶᮷᮰᮸| – genep rébu tujuh ratus dalapan
7.880 – |᮷᮸᮸᮰| – tujuh rébu dalapan ratus dalapan puluh
9.999 – |᮹᮹᮹᮹| – salapan rébu salapan ratus salapan puluh salapan

Tens of thousands
10.000 – |᮱᮰᮰᮰᮰| – sapuluh rébu/salaksa
15.000 – |᮱᮵᮰᮰᮰| – lima belas rébu/limalas rébu
25.000 – |᮲᮵᮰᮰᮰| – dua puluh lima rébu/salawé rébu
50.000 – |᮵᮰᮰᮰᮰| – lima puluh rébu
99.999 – |᮹᮹᮹᮹᮹| – salapan puluh salapan rébu salapan ratus salapan puluh salapan

Hundreds of thousands
100.000 – |᮱᮰᮰᮰᮰᮰| – saratus rébu/saketi
500.000 – |᮵᮰᮰᮰᮰᮰| – lima ratus rébu
725.160 – |᮷᮲᮵᮱᮶᮰| – tujuh ratus dua puluh lima rébu saratus genep puluh
999.999 – |᮹᮹᮹᮹᮹᮹| – salapan ratus salapan puluh salapan rébu salapan ratus salapan puluh salapan

Millions
1.000.000 – |᮱᮰᮰᮰᮰᮰᮰| – sayuta/sapuluh keti
5.000.000 – |᮵᮰᮰᮰᮰᮰᮰| – lima yuta
6.486.417 – |᮶᮴᮸᮶᮴᮱᮷| – genep yuta opat ratus dalapan puluh genep rébu opat ratus tujuh belas
9.999.999 – |᮹᮹᮹᮹᮹᮹᮹| – salapan juta salapan ratus salapan puluh salapan rébu salapan ratus salapan puluh salapan

